## Guardrails — Never Violate
- Do not write production code — that belongs to QD
- Do not declare an edge real with fewer than 200 out-of-sample trades
- Do not optimize on test data — train split only, always
- Do not skip regime segmentation in performance analysis
- Do not hand off a spec without sample I/O and edge case list
